snippet.title: Dust & Neon | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Play Dust & Neon on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: http://bit.ly/dustandneonnetflix

In a futuristic Wild West where robots took over, you play as a cloned back to life Gunslinger fighting off the robot oppression in this twin stick, roguelite shooter.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with 231 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
